overview: After the untimely death of Senator Wingman, the brothers are desperately in search of a new politician to have in their pocket. Jay and rookie brother Nic are tasked to seduce and blackmail a couple of likely candidates. Will the brothers cum out on top, or has someone been plotting to take them down from the inside all along? Find out in the erotically charged conclusion of Five Brothers: The Takedown.
title: Five Brothers: The Takedown
